Package org.neo4j.common

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DependencyResolver
    Find a dependency given a type.
    DependencyResolver.SelectionStrategy
    Responsible for making the choice between available candidates.
    DependencySatisfier
    Able to satisfy dependencies, later needed to be resolved by for example a DependencyResolver.
    ProgressReporter
    Progress indicator to track progress of long running processes.
    TokenNameLookup
    Lookup of names from token ids.
    Validator<T>
    Validates a value, throws IllegalArgumentException for invalid values.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DependencyResolver.Adapter
    Adapter for DependencyResolver which will select the first available candidate by default for DependencyResolver.Adapter.resolveDependency(Class).
    HexPrinter
    Prints streams of bytes as hex, printed in columns and rows neatly ordered.
    Subject
    A representation of originator of actions in the database.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Edition  
    EntityType
    Type of graph entity.
